                "text": "Levy MM, Fink MP, Marshall JC, et al. 2001 SCCM/ESICM/ACCP/ATS/SIS International Sepsis Definitions Conference. Crit Care Med. 2003;31(4):1250–1256."
            }
        ],
        "evidence": "<p>Series of Yes/No questions.</p>",
        "facts": "<ul>\n<li>SIRS - 2 YES answers meets criteria.</li>\n<li>Sepsis Criteria - 2 YES of SIRS + Suspected Source of Infection.</li>\n<li>Severe Sepsis Criteria - 2 YES of SIRS + Lactic Acidosis, SBP.</li>\n<li>Multiple Organ Dysfunction Syndrome - 2 YES of SIRS + Evidence of &ge; 2 Organs Failing.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Check with your own hospital for its sepsis guidelines, sepsis 'bundle' or sepsis algorithm. Two excellent sepsis references (<a href=\"https://emcrit.org/severe-sepsis-resources/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">1</a>, <a href=\"https://crashingpatient.com/wp-content/pdf/Loma%20Linda%20STOP%20Sepsis%20Bundle.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2</a>) come from the <a href=\"https://emcrit.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">EMCrit</a> website.</p>",
        "estimation": [],
        "primary_complains": [
            "Fever"
        ],
        "disease_treated": [
            "Coronavirus",
            "COVID-19",
            "Sepsis"
        ],
        "logic": "var calc_output=[];\nvar mini_msg=''; \nvar msgadd='';\nvar msg='';\n\nif(parseFloat(temperature)+parseFloat(heart_rate)+parseFloat(respiratory_rate)+parseFloat(white_blood_cell_count)>=2){\n  mini_msg='Meets SIRS criteria'; \n  msg='This patient meets SIRS criteria.';\n  if(parseFloat(infection)==1){\n    mini_msg='Meets sepsis criteria'; \n    msg='This patient meets sepsis criteria.';\n    msgadd=' Follow your guidelines for sepsis, which typically include aggressive fluid resuscitation, early, broad-spectrum antibiotics, ICU consultation, CVP evaluation, and occasionally pressors and transfusion.';}\n  if(parseFloat(lactic_acidosis)==1){\n    mini_msg='Severe sepsis'; \n    msg='This patient meets severe sepsis criteria.';\n  }\n  if(parseFloat(severe_sepsis)==1){\n    mini_msg='Septic shock'; \n    msg='This patient meets septic shock criteria.';\n  }if(parseFloat(organ_failure)==1){\n    mini_msg='Multi-organ dysfunction'; \n    msg='This patient meets multiple organ dysfunction syndrome.';\n}}\nelse{\n  mini_msg='Does not meet SIRS'; \n  msg='This patient does not meet SIRS criteria. For other causes of shock, see the Next Steps section.';\n}\n\nmsg+=msgadd; \n\ncalc_output.push({\n  name:'mini',\n  value:' ',\n  value_text:' ',\n  message:mini_msg\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n  name:'1096_SIRS & Sepsis Criteria_result',\n  value:' ',\n  value_text:' ',\n  message:msg\n}); \n",
